{"article_id":"s2XzUpigh4iEhz40","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A bill","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"providing $ 1.375 billion for a physical barrier along the U.S.-Mexico border","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"easily cleared Congress on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"and is heading to President Donald Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"who is expected to sign it","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"and then declare a national emergency","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"to get more funding for his promised border wall .","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"\" President Trump will sign the government funding bill ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"as he has stated before ,","depth":13},{"id":11,"text":"he will also take other executive action","depth":14},{"id":12,"text":"- including a national emergency -","depth":14},{"id":13,"text":"to ensure","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"we stop the national security and humanitarian crisis at the border , ''","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"White House press secretary Sarah Sanders said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"The stunning announcement came","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"just before the Senate voted 83-16 to approve the funding measure ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"which will avert another government shutdown","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"and offer $ 1.375 billion for a 55-mile border barrier","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"- much less than the $ 5.7 billion","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"that Trump has demanded for a wall along the southern border .","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"Hours later , the Housevoted 300-128 to approve thebill","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and send it to Trump .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Trump is expected to sign the measure on Friday","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"and at the same time declare a national emergency","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"to access additional funds for a border wall .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Late Thursday , the White House announced","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the president would be making remarks about national security and the southern border in the Rose Garden at 10 a.m. EST .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"His decision","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to declare a national emergency","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"angered Democrats and even some members of his own party","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and set the stage for a possible legal challenge .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"At a news conference , House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , railed against the possibility","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"of Trump declaring a national emergency ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"saying","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Republicans \" should have some dismay to the door","depth":14},{"id":37,"text":"that they are opening ,","depth":14},{"id":38,"text":"the threshold","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"they are crossing . \"","depth":14},{"id":40,"text":"\" The precedent","depth":15},{"id":41,"text":"that the president is setting here","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"is something","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"that should be met with great unease and dismay by the Republicans","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"and , of course , we will respond accordingly , \"","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"Pelosi said .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"an emergency declaration opens the door","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"for other presidents to do \" an end run around Congress . \"","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"\" Just think of what a president with different values can present to the American people , \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"Pelosi added .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"She did n't say specifically","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"how Democrats would respond","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"but said","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"that they would \" review our options . \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , said","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"that Trump declaring a national emergency would be `` a tremendous mistake '' and `` a gross abuse of the power of the presidency ''","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to distract from the fact","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that he failed to deliver on his campaign promise","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"that he 'd make Mexico pay for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"But Sen. John Kennedy , R-La. ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who voted for the bill ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"he supports Trump ' s plan","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"to declare an emergency .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"\" The president ' s not exercising any power","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that Congress didn ' t give him , ' '","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"Kennedy said .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"\" Had Congress done its job","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"instead of playing politics ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"he wouldn ' t have to do it . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Earlier Thursday , before the White House announcement , lawmakers were praying","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"Trump would sign the funding bill .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"Literally .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Just after the morning prayer in the Senate , Sen. Chuck Grassley , R-Iowa , added a quick prayer of his own :","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"`` Let 's all pray","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"that the president will have wisdom","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to sign the bill ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"so the government doesn ' t shut down . ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"Trump 's emergency declaration would trigger a drawn out legal fight","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"The legislation ,","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"which was released late Wednesday night ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"would spend $ 1.375 billion","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to fund the barrier along the Texas border .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"It requires","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"the structure be made of previously deployed designs .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"That rules out concrete ,","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"but it can be made of steel slats .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"The agreement also provides $ 7.6 billion for the Immigration and Customs Enforcement .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Some of that would go toward funding a goal of 40,520 detention beds by the end of the year .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"That number is what was previously appropriated","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"but ICE had exceeded it ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"detaining closer to 50,000 people .","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"ICE can not use the funding","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"to hire more people","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"to apprehend and remove undocumented immigrants .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"The bill won the support from the majority of both parties ,","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"but some conservatives and progressives announced","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"they would vote no .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"`` The Department of Homeland Security does not deserve an increase in funding , ''","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"Democratic Reps. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez of New York , Ilhan Omar of Minnesota , Ayanna Pressley of Massachusetts and Rashida Tlaib of Michigan said in a joint statement Thursday","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"announcing their intention to vote against the legislation .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Ahead of the Senate vote , some faith leaders gathered across from the Capitol","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"to protest funding","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"included in the measure","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"for a barrier and more detention beds .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"They urged lawmakers to instead work on legislation","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"to better protect immigrants .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"\" If we have $ 5 billion","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that we can find ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"we ought to spend it on reunifying those children","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"who were separated at the border","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"instead of building a wall","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that ' s not going to do anything for anybody","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"except perhaps to stroke someone ' s ego and someone ' s racist white supremacist ideology , \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"said the Rev . Leslie Copeland-Tune , director of the Ecumenical Advocacy Days for Global Peace with Justice .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"The group later visited the offices of congressional leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"including Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell ,","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"where they prayed in the lobby .","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"How congressional Democrats could fight a Trump wall national emergency declaration","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"Trump ' s demand for a border wall","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"- a signature promise of his presidential campaign -","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"was at the center of a budget standoff","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"that triggered a record 35-day government shutdown late last year .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"The shutdown ended in late January","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"when lawmakers passed a temporary funding bill","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"to buy them time","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"to work out an agreement on border security .","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"On Monday , a bipartisan group of budget negotiators from the House and Senate announced an agreement \" in principle \" on the border security deal .","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"Trump has suggested","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"he could get the rest of the money for a wall","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"by declaring some sort of a \" national emergency \"","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"- allowing him , in theory , to use defense money for wall construction ,","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"but also inviting legal challenges from opponents","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"who say","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"the president lacks the legal authority","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"to declare an emergency in this case .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Members of the hard-line House Freedom Caucus , a conservative group close to the president , sent a letter Thursday","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"urging him to use his executive powers","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"to declare a national emergency","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"and build the rest of the wall .","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"`` The conference committee deal is bad , ''","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"the group wrote .","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"`` If you feel the need","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"to sign the legislation ,","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"we also urge you to immediately use your authority ...","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"to access funds","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"to begin building a much-needed border wall. ``","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"Acting White House chief of staff Mick Mulvaney and other officials also have suggested another option :","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"moving existing money from other accounts","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"to fund walls , fences or other sorts of barriers .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"Trump must sign the new border security bill by midnight Friday","depth":6},{"id":154,"text":"or federal funding will lapse ,","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"triggering another government shutdown .","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":157,"text":"What to know about national emergencies and their role in US history","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"More :","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"Government shutdown stymied frozen tax refunds ,","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"tied up IRS phone lines ,","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"report shows","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"More :","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"In government shutdown aftermath , federal workers still hurting ,","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"survey finds","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":166,"text":"Lawmakers do n't want any more government shutdowns ;","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"they just ca n't agree on how to prevent them","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":335,"left":0,"right":334,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":334,"left":286,"right":333,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":286,"left":245,"right":285,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":245,"left":237,"right":244,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":237,"left":193,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":190,"right":192,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":182,"right":189,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":174,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":170,"right":173,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":170,"left":169,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":169,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":4,"right":172,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":5,"right":171,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":171,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":8,"right":179,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":179,"left":9,"right":178,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"left":176,"right":177,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":10,"right":175,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":175,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":189,"left":187,"rig